The paper proposes a machine learning approach for inferring LI-RADS categorization from ultrasound reports, which involves natural language processing and image analysis. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
